persons:
    person-qotho:
        properties:
            gender: male
            name:
                value: Qotho
                fields:
                    given: Qotho
            house: Dothraki
        notes: "One of Khal Drogo's three bloodriders. He had cruel eyes and quick hands that liked to hurt; he left bruises on the handmaid Doreah and made Irri sob in the night. Even his horses seemed to fear him. He helped restrain Viserys Targaryen during his execution."
